    <item>
      <title>澳元和新西兰元有望因加息押注而跑赢全球其他货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/aussie-kiwi-set-to-outperform-global-peers-on-rates-hike-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于澳大利亚和新西兰央行推迟降息，这两个货币免受政治风险上升的影响，因此这两个货币的表现有望优于全球其他货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/aussie-kiwi-set-to-outperform-global-peers-on-rates-hike-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>本周全球大宗商品市场值得关注的五大关键图表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国农民正在囤积玉米，就像 1988 年那样。投资者押注欧洲天然气价格将继续攀升，这表明市场预计未来几个月供应将收紧。而飓风贝里尔如此早就出现在大西洋上，其罕见的强度预示着未来可能出现超级风暴季节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
